	measure Qty_Latest_V = ```
			
			VAR LatestVersion = 
			    CALCULATE(
			        MAX('fact_flat_forecast_actual'[name_version]),
			        ALLSELECTED('fact_flat_forecast_actual')
			    )
			VAR YearMonthText = MID(LatestVersion, 3, 9)
			VAR YearText = MID(YearMonthText, 3,6)
			VAR MonthText = RIGHT(YearMonthText, 2)
			
			VAR DATE_VERSION =
			    DATE(
			        VALUE(YearText),
			        VALUE(MonthText),
			        1
			    )
			
			RETURN
			IF(
			    MAX('fact_flat_forecast_actual'[dt_fsc_month_last]) >= DATE_VERSION,
			    CALCULATE(
			        SUM('fact_flat_forecast_actual'[qty]),
			        'fact_flat_forecast_actual'[name_version] = LatestVersion
			    ),
			    BLANK()
			)
			```
		displayFolder: 1. Main KPIs - Forecast Accuracy
		lineageTag: 8db59774-8e5d-42eb-892c-307226212ea8

		annotation PBI_FormatHint = {"isGeneralNumber":true}

